<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c594d2df83.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/arithmetic-styles.css"> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar-styles.css">
     <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico?v=1.1">
    <title>Science</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Free Trial Form</h1>
        <p>Before you fill in the form, you may first want to read our rules and regulations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container mb-3">
      <form action="/trial/new" method="post">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="outlet" class="form-label" >Outlet</label>
          <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example" name="outlet">
            <option selected>Choose</option>
            <option value="1">Toa Payoh</option>
            <option value="2">Hougang</option>
            <option value="3">Private</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="outlet" class="form-label" >Timing</label>
          <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example" name="timing">
            <option selected>?</option>
          </select>
          <div><b>*Note that the free trial timing reflected are identical to the available slots.</b></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="otherTiming" class="form-label" name="otherTiming">Other Timing</label>
           <input type="text" class="form-control" name="otherTiming" placeholder="If there is no situable timing. Please fill in your preferred day and timing. Thanks!">
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <!-- <label for="subject" class="form-label" name="subject">Subject</label> -->
          <p>Subject</p>
          <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault" name="subject">
          <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">Standard Math</label>
          <input class="form-check-input ms-3" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault" name="subject">
          <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">Foundation Math</label>
          <input class="form-check-input ms-3" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault" name="subject">
          <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">Standard Science</label>
          <input class="form-check-input ms-3" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault" name="subject">
          <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">Foundation Science</label>
        </div>

        <h1>Details</h1>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <h4>Student</h4>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="childName" class="form-label">Name</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="childName">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="childSurname" class="form-label">Surname</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="childSurname"> 
           </div>
           <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="DOB" class="form-label">Date of birth</label>
            <input type="date" class="form-control" name="DOB"> 
           </div>
           <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="gender" class="form-label">Gender</label>
            <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example"name="gender">
              <option selected>Choose</option>
              <option value="1">Male</option>
              <option value="2">famale</option>
            </select>
          </div>
           <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="school" class="form-label">School</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="school"> 
           </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col">
            <h4>Parent/Guardian 1</h4>
           <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="parentOneName" class="form-label">Name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="parentOneName">
            <!-- <div name="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="parentOneSurname" class="form-label">Surname</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="parentOneSurname">
            <!-- <div name="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="roleOne" class="form-label">Role</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="roleOne" placeholder="Father / Mother etc">
            <!-- <div id="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="ContactOne" class="form-label">Contact Number</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="ContactOne">
            <!-- <div id="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email">
            <!-- <div id="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
            <div class="col">
              <h4>Parent/Guardian 2</h4>
              <div class="mb-3">
                  <label for="parentTwoSurname" class="form-label">Name</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" name="parentTwoSurname">
             </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="parentTwoSurname" class="form-label">Surname</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="parentTwoSurname">
              <!-- <div id="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="roleTwo" class="form-label">Role</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="roleTwo" placeholder="Father / Mother etc">
              <!-- <div id="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="ContactTwo" class="form-label">Contact Number</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="ContactTwo">
              <!-- <div id="parentName" class="form-text">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</div> -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1>Questions</h1>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="questionA" class="form-label">Does your child have any learning disabilities?</label>
          <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="questionA" placeholder="If no, leave blank. If yes, please tells us what disability"></textarea>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="questionB" class="form-label">Is this your child's first time attending tuition for the subject that you are interested in signing him/her up for?</label>
        <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="questionB" placeholder="If yes, leave blank. If no, please tells why you did not continue there?"></textarea>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="questionC" class="form-label">What should we do if your child misbehavies?</label>
        <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="questionC" placeholder="Fill in the blank"></textarea>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="questionD" class="form-label" >Do you allow physical punishment?</label>
        <select class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example" name="questionD">
          <option selected>Choose</option>
          <option value="1">Yes</option>
          <option value="2">No</option>
          <!-- <option value="3">Private</option> -->
        </select>
      </div>

        <h1>Rules and Regulations</h1>
        <ul>
          <li><h4>Payment and fees</h4></li>
          <div class="ms-3">
              <p>Please check with the admin staff as the amount is subjected to change.</p>
          </div>
          <li><h4>Class Size</h4></li>
            <div class="ms-3">
              <p>3 pax to 5 pax.</p>
              <p>A maximum size of 3 but allow 2 more pax for either extra or make up lessons.</p>
            </div>
          <li><h4>Absence / Sick</h4></li>
            <div class="ms-3">
              <p>Please inform the tutor at least 2 hours in advance and arrange for make up.</p>
            </div>
          <li><h4>Make up lessons</h4></li>
            <div class="ms-3">
              <p>Make up lessons will expire within 1 month of occurence, and cannot be used to offset next month's fees.</p>
            </div>
          <li><h4>Public Holiday</h4></li>
            <div class="ms-3">
              <p>Assume that classes will still continue except for Chinese New Year or unless specificied otherwise.</p>
              <p>If you choose to not attend, please inform and arrange for make up.</p>
            </div>
          <li><h4>Bringing forward of lessons</h4></li>
          <div class="ms-3">
              <p>Lessons from school holidays period would usually be brought forward to the earlier months to better prepare your child for the upcoming exams.</p>
              <p>Those "extra" lessons will only need to be paid during its actual month.</p>
              <p><i>eg. Lessons from June Holidays brought forward into May only needs to be paid when June comes around.</i></p>
          </div>
         </ul>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>

     </form>
</div>
 
</body>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-HwwvtgBNo3bZJJLYd8oVXjrBZt8cqVSpeBNS5n7C8IVInixGAoxmnlMuBnhbgrkm" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</html>